// src/gateway/routes/chat.router.ts
- If this request needs 2+ tool calls ... call declare_plan FIRST ...
+ Use declare_plan FIRST only for complex, multi-phase work ... Do NOT call declare_plan for quick linear actions ... Needing 2+ tools alone is not sufficient.

// src/gateway/tools/defs/agent-team-schedule.ts
- Call this FIRST whenever you need 2 or more tool calls.
+ Call this FIRST only when the task has meaningful phases ... Do NOT use for quick linear actions even if they require multiple tools.

// src/gateway/comms/telegram-channel.ts
+ For quick linear Telegram actions, do not declare a plan; reserve declare_plan for complex multi-phase tasks.

